	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Most certainly!
<br />Super Mario Bros 3 uses the grayscale bit when you complete a fortress level (to flash the screen gray several times).
<br />Final Fantasy 1 uses an interesting cycle-timed trick using grayscale to make a diagonal beam of light when you use a particular item.
<br />There are probably plenty of others I don't know about...

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


